	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Someone's found a prototype cartridge of SimCity!!<br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7-M_LcqJsc" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V7-M_LcqJsc</a><br /><br />Been hoping this would appear for a long time now. I'm excited to finally hear the music from it especially.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


